readme:
# Data Class Package

To accompany the "Data Class" mobile application, this "desktop companion" IDE plugin has been developed. It allows users to automatically import all key and helper libraries required for Data Analysis, to read data from a csv file into a data frame, and due to its its integration with PasteBin it allows pulling code directly from PasteBin by typing the code snippet's PasteBin ID into the editor.

To find out more about Data Class, please visit [data-class.ml](https://data-class.ml).


![Demo GIF of the Package](https://github.com/svavaroutas/data-class/raw/master/demo.gif)
